### Update a crisp
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/crisps/69adecb85c5e3d4cc186cd00
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 1.45
}

### Delete a crisp
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/crisps/69adecb85c5e3d4cc186cd00